OL,3,CMan jailed after using dog lead to
OL,4,Cpunch victim in the head
OL,6,FA man who used a dog lead to punch his
OL,7,Fvictim in the head has been jailed.
OL,9,FBenjamin Crofts, 27, admitted to
OL,10,Finflicting grievous bodily harm as he
OL,11,Fappeared at Caernarfon Crown Court on
OL,12,FAugust 14.
OL,14,FCrofts, of Tan Y Bryn Road,
OL,15,FMaesgeirchen, Bangor, became involved
OL,16,Fin a verbal altercation with another
OL,17,Fman on Holyhead Road in Bangor during
OL,18,Fthe early hours of May 1.
