OL,3,CMan jailed after using dog lead to
OL,4,Cpunch victim in the head
OL,6,FHe then removed his dog's lead from
OL,7,Fits collar, wrapped it around his hand
OL,8,Fand punched the man to the head.
OL,10,FThe victim became unconscious after
OL,11,Ffalling backwards and hitting his head
OL,12,Fon the kerb. He was later taken to
OL,13,Fhospital where it was confirmed he had
OL,14,Fa significant bleed on the brain and a
OL,15,Fskull fracture.
OL,17,FCrofts fled the scene but was quickly
OL,18,Flocated and arrested by police
OL,19,Fofficers. He was jailed for one year
OL,20,Fand 11 months.
