OL,3,CMan jailed after using dog lead to
OL,4,Cpunch victim in the head
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Geraint Jones said:
OL,7,F"Violence of any kind is never
OL,8,Facceptable and will not be tolerated
OL,9,Fin north Wales.
OL,11,F"Crofts' malicious actions caused
OL,12,Fserious injuries that will have a
OL,13,Flasting impact (on) his victim and
OL,14,Ftheir family.
OL,16,F"One punch can kill, and it is lucky
OL,17,Fthat there weren't fatal consequences
OL,18,Fon this occasion."
